Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper investigates the presence of Gestalt phenomena in image recognition networks. 
2. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also likely as the paper focuses on feedforward image classification neural networks. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the training and generalization abilities of the neural networks. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper investigates the cognitive abilities of neural networks. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper compares the closure effect in neural networks to human perception.
